268
00:08:48,533 --> 00:08:49,733
<b>including their right to</b>

269
00:08:49,733 --> 00:08:50,966
<b>return to Diego Garcia."</b>

270
00:08:51,433 --> 00:08:52,566
<b>There's a £40 million</b>

271
00:08:52,566 --> 00:08:54,733
<b>trust fund for the Chagossians.</b>

272
