<b>Chagossian Voices opposed the deal</b>

281
00:09:12,033 --> 00:09:13,133
<b>because it doesn't include</b>

282
00:09:13,133 --> 00:09:14,466
<b>the full right of return.</b>

283
00:09:14,833 --> 00:09:16,866
<b>Legal analysts note the resettlement</b>

284
00:09:16,866 --> 00:09:19,433
<b>clause is in substance declaratory.</b>

285
00:09:19,899 --> 00:09:20,733
<b>It doesn't actually</b>

286
00:09:20,733 --> 00:09:22,199
<b>secure the right to return.</b>

287
00:09:22,766 --> 00:09:24,699
<b>It just says Mauritius is free to</b>

288
00:09:24,699 --> 00:09:25,800
<b>implement a program.</b>

289
00:09:26,533 --> 00:09:28,266
<b>That's not exactly the same thing.</b>

290
00:09:28,766 --> 00:09:30,699
<b>Diego Garcia remains exactly what the</b>

291
