<b>But look at what actually changed.</b>

304
00:09:57,533 --> 00:10:00,166
<b>In 1965, Britain controlled the islands.</b>

305
00:10:00,666 --> 00:10:02,166
<b>The Chagossians couldn't go home.</b>

306
