<b>controls the islands on paper.</b>

308
00:10:06,833 --> 00:10:08,566
<b>Britain still controls Diego Garcia.</b>

309
00:10:09,266 --> 00:10:11,533
<b>The Chagossians still can't go home.</b>

310
00:10:11,733 --> 00:10:13,466
<b>The UK calls it making amends.</b>

311
00:10:13,933 --> 00:10:15,566
<b>Mauritius calls it a great victory.</b>

312
00:10:15,866 --> 00:10:17,500
<b>But neither government asked the</b>

313
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,899
<b>Chagossians what they wanted.</b>

314
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,533
<b>The flag over Diego</b>

315
00:10:20,533 --> 00:10:22,600
<b>Garcia will change eventually.</b>

316
00:10:23,133 --> 00:10:24,199
<b>The base stays.</b>

317
